                            <comment id="13778964" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 16:54:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We already have these two:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;cassandra  -  memlock  unlimited
cassandra  -  nofile   100000
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;32k threads seems a little overboard.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13940485" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 19 Mar 2014 14:06:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed the address space change as unlimited, and nproc at the reasonable bound of 8096, since going beyond that would suggest that either you need HSHA, or mask a bug on our side.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
